    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there’s no point in rebuilding anything. like, why bother? everything i built was with them. the house, the plans, the future... it's all just rubble now. it's not just sadness, it's like this constant, crushing weight that makes it hard to even breathe. i'm just so tired of fighting it.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
